                title="Secure AWS S3 Bucket Configuration",
                description="Fix common S3 misconfigurations and implement defense-in-depth.",
                environment="AWS Free Tier account, AWS CLI, Python with boto3, public S3 bucket test.",
                tasks=[
                    "Audit existing S3 bucket permissions and policies",
                    "Enable Block Public Access at account and bucket level",
                    "Implement bucket policy with least privilege",
